### Discovery dashboard
GET http://localhost:8761

### Gateway: list events
GET http://localhost:8080/api/events

### Gateway: list seats
GET http://localhost:8080/api/shows/show-2026-07-01/seats

### Event service: list events
GET http://localhost:8091/api/events

### Event service: list seats
GET http://localhost:8091/api/shows/show-2026-07-01/seats

### Booking service: hold seat with pessimistic lock
POST http://localhost:8092/api/bookings/hold
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "alice",
  "showId": "show-2026-07-01",
  "seatCode": "A-1",
  "strategy": "PESSIMISTIC",
  "holdSeconds": 120
}

### Gateway: hold seat with pessimistic lock
POST http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/hold
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "gateway-alice",
  "showId": "show-2026-07-01",
  "seatCode": "A-4",
  "strategy": "PESSIMISTIC",
  "holdSeconds": 120
}

### Booking service: hold seat with optimistic lock
POST http://localhost:8092/api/bookings/hold
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "bob",
  "showId": "show-2026-07-01",
  "seatCode": "A-2",
  "strategy": "OPTIMISTIC",
  "holdSeconds": 120
}

### Booking service: hold seat with redis lock
POST http://localhost:8092/api/bookings/hold
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "carol",
  "showId": "show-2026-07-01",
  "seatCode": "A-3",
  "strategy": "REDIS_HOLD",
  "holdSeconds": 120
}

### Payment service: simulate success
POST http://localhost:8093/api/payments/simulate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingNo": "BOOK-REPLACE-ME",
  "delayMillis": 0,
  "forceFailure": false,
  "forceTimeout": false
}

### Booking service: pay booking
POST http://localhost:8092/api/bookings/BOOK-REPLACE-ME/pay
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingNo": "BOOK-REPLACE-ME",
  "delayMillis": 0,
  "forceFailure": false,
  "forceTimeout": false
}

### Booking service: get booking
GET http://localhost:8092/api/bookings/BOOK-REPLACE-ME

### Booking service: cancel booking
POST http://localhost:8092/api/bookings/BOOK-REPLACE-ME/cancel

### Booking service: scan expired holds
POST http://localhost:8092/api/admin/expiry/scan

### Booking service: race metrics
GET http://localhost:8092/api/admin/metrics/race-summary

### Gateway: race metrics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/metrics/race-summary

### Simulator: run concurrent race
POST http://localhost:8094/api/admin/simulator/run
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "showId": "show-2026-07-01",
  "seatCode": "A-1",
  "concurrency": 100,
  "strategy": "OPTIMISTIC",
  "holdSeconds": 30
}

### Gateway: run concurrent race
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/simulator/run
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "showId": "show-2026-07-01",
  "seatCode": "A-5",
  "concurrency": 100,
  "strategy": "OPTIMISTIC",
  "holdSeconds": 30
}
